        <abstract>
            <p>CD lost first round of nominations at the Académie Française to Jean-Frédéric de Brandt. QdeB and Milne-Edwards continue the battle, but CD is fiercely attacked.</p>
            <p>Asks for complete citation of CD’s geological work on South America because it has to be shown he did more than collect objects.</p>
